project_descr: This project aims at developing capacities of Federal, State and local level governance to combat the Avian Influenza Crisis

outputs.output_descr: Federal, State and local level governance capacities developed to combat the Avian Influenza Crisis;in-house capacity of UNDP strengthened to respond to the crisis and intra-UN procedures strengthened to move the UN towards a joint program in responding to the crisis

project_title: undp response to avian influenza crisis, nigeria
